Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been her own inexperience\Nthat caused the tragic incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the young life lost\Non the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...was not a small misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody could hope to comfort\Nthe grief-stricken Kai Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base was now above\Nthe South American continent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...on its way to Jaburo, the\NFederation Forces headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragedy in Jaburo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it.\NThe Trojan Horse is headed for Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just as our spy reported. Don't lose them.\N- Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Butterfly! Butterfly! Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Butter... fly! Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- They're so beautiful...\N- Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've finally made it\Nto the Federation Forces' dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't like it?\N- I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention all hands!\NWe're entering Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watching for any enemy aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we're entering Jaburo,\Nbut I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Landing completed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse's signal disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we've finally located\Nthe biggest entrance to Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Conduct a thorough search of the area\Nwhere the Trojan Horse disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crush the ship and the Jaburo base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage is quite extensive.\NWorse than what they reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the White Base has certainly seen\Na lot of heavy combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Commence inspection!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence inspection procedures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First and second teams,\Nprepare for inspection!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Captain Woody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Bright Noa,\Nchief officer of the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a young man here\Nnamed Amuro Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's Amuro?!\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected somebody so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the pilot of the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda told me a lot about you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda told you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- And what is it?\N- They called it a Zock. Mobile Suit Zock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amphibious, with a jumping capability\Nseveral times that of a Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineers at North America's\NCalifornia Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it isn't just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as the reinforcements arrive\Nfrom the California Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll send our second attack team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go as an advance party, so carry out\Nyour mission to the best of your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected a physical examination\Nto be such a chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Amuro, your exam was especially long.\NWas there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. They were all busy checking\Nbrain waves and taking x-rays and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They told me I'm physically healthy\Nand mentally sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This medical facility is perfectly\Nfurnished with everything imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's nothing wrong with us!\N- Don't wanna! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Katz, Letz, please keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with these bodies? Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't have any cavities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Woody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to get some rest, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Supervision is a thankless job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do anything to help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're at Jaburo,\Nyou can relax and leave it all to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. Did you know Lt. Matilda well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After Operation Odessa was over...\Nwe were planning to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We expected that the White Base\Nwould arrive at Jaburo in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...so Matilda had hoped to have\Nthe crew attend our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,l-ls that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry, Captain Woody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd only known how to use\Nthe Gundam better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...then Ms. Matilda wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so conceited, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam alone can't win the war,\Nnor could it have saved Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If a pilot fights\Nas best he can in each battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...and doesn't do anything\Nthat he'd later regret... that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the White Base because I know\NMatilda cared so much about this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm doing my best\Nto get it fully repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us are doing our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it. The main entrance to Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't got a metallic reaction,\NI would have missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That means they'd never\Nlaunch an attack here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't want anyone\Nto see through the camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, the White Base corps\Nshall continue their mission as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you will be assigned\Nto the Tianem fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...but official notification will only be\Ngiven just before the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. What should we do in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest up in your assigned quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you will not be penalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai, please consider it as\Nour repaying a favor to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To this day, we regret the Federation's loss\Nof such a valuable politician...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If your father were alive today,\Nyou wouldn't have had to emigrate to Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir, I would rather not discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy approaching hatches 231 and 243\Nof the South Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take level 2 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another patrol?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you may return to your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to alert status, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Lt. Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must apologize for bringing a force\Nthat's too small for a first-wave attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no problem. How long until\Nwe reach Jaburo, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Less than an hour.\N- Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Should we attack?\N- No, that'd reveal our location. Hold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two are Goggs, for underwater combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one isn't in the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A new model of mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention all units in Jaburo's South Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to level 2 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm going ahead.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do it.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are you going?\N- The White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's taking level 2 battle stations,\Nso where else are we going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- The others are coming as well.\N- Yes. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many went up?\N- I'm not sure, but there were at least four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one is authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The others are for camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!\NSwitch to level 1 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal flare confirmed at bearing 128.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! We've been ordered\Nto take level 1 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting the crew aboard the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finished repairs on the mobile suits\Nbut the White Base itself isn't operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, Mirai! Get intel from\NGeneral HQ as quickly as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make a move until\Nwe know what's going on out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,General HQ, how is the enemy deployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Can we launch?\N- Sir! We can guard the entrance to Jaburo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll send Amuro and Sayla In the G-Bull.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that! Send out Kai and Hayato\Nin the Guncannon and Guntank! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe those Zeons\Nfollowed us all the way out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu. I won't mope about any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll totally crush the Zeons, so people\Nwon't have to suffer like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guntank, Hayato, rolling out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Amuro! Ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}G- Bull, Sayla and Amuro, launching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Let's stay close to\NJaburo's entranceway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy will try to force their way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those... Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Those are GMs,\Nthe Gundam's mass-production type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First wave of Zakus,in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain Char,your Z'Gok team last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Lt. Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Hwan! Jittal! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stay close to me.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already lost Li Hwan!\NJaburo is well defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How many mobile suits will land safely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! J-Jittal, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's vital that I join up\Nwith the advance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like 28 mobile suits have landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a large force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I believe it's still too small\Nto fight against all of Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only targeting A Block\Nwhere the spaceship dock is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- The White Base must have been followed.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the White Base will always be\Na nuisance to the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't heard anything\Nat all from General HQ, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch all monitors over\Nto external surveillance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,General HQ will hear from me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a situation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we carelessly go outside, that willance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea what the enemy is doing,\Nso there's no way for us to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we moved out and found the enemy\Nin front of us, we'd be toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even avenge Miharu, can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming... Damn Zeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boraskyniv. How are things proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! We just finished setting the explosives.\NShould we break in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not yet. Are we going from the front?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Any other entrances?\N- There's a smaller entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...about 500 meters upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... We'll attack both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The two Goggs will breach this entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boraskyniv and I will break through\Nthe one upstream. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're here! It's the Zeons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They allowed the Zeons to break through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Workers, join the defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda sacrificed her life\Nto protect the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I'll let it be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get close to the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One Gogg destroyed!\NKai took it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Ms. Sayla! The G-Bull must turn back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy broke through another entrance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's leave the rest to Mr. Kai and Hayato.\N- Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems many have broken through, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our White Base you're attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! Instruct the G-Bull\Nto change to the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy mobile suits are advancing quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Bull! G-Bull!\NPlease Convert to Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger! What's Invading??{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,B Deck! Please send out G-Armor's B-Parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A hovercraft is no use here! Please fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's Captain Woody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Don't do it!\NF-Fall back now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A red mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a Zaku.\NBut could the red mobile suit mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Char's in it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A GM!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't close in carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake... It's him...\NHe's come back to fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it... That's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you, Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten even better, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Zeons!\NGet out of Jaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Woody! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Woody...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The main camera has been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Boraskyniv! Do you read me?!\NI need some backup now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way. I'm taking out Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That mobile suit... I'm certain it was Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So Char has pursued us\Nall the way to Jaburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Do you read me? Are you all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I let one mobile suit escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did very well.f the enemy force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they did a lot of damage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Woody was a casualty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have cared about the White Base\Neven more than we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...That's how it seemed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Men can feel emotion\Nso strongly sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that true?\N- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... And Char's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Char? Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I only saw a red mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm positive that it was Char,\Nthe Red Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would ever call Katz, Letz and Kikka\N"nothing but a nuisance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And who will find the enemy's time bombs\Nin time to save Jaburo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Char and Sayla meet...\Nfor the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NA Wish of War Orphans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Wish of War Orphans
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
